{{menutrail|Main menu}}
The '''new game''' menu technically corresponds to the sequence of the [[class selection menu]], the [[episode selection menu]] and the [[skill selection menu]]. When one of these three menus has only one item to choose from, this item is automatically selected without displaying the menu. The new game menu can be summoned with the <tt>menu_game</tt> [[console command]].
